        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to ensure that a Federal employee who takes leave without pay in order to perform service as a member of the uniformed services or member of the National  Guard shall continue to receive pay in an amount  which, when  taken together with the pay and allowances such individual is receiving for such service, will be no less than the basic pay such individual would then be receiving  if no interruption in employment had occurred.</title>
